<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/20287740" target="_blank" data-id="295355" data-za-element-name="Title">
Web 前端开发前景如何？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/20287740/answer/16618002">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="1778855">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="16618002"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
