<div class="feed-main">
<div class="content">
<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/26644904" target="_blank" data-id="2840995" data-za-element-name="Title">
2014 年末有哪些比较火的 Web 开发技术？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/26644904/answer/35353767">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="9530033">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="35353767"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>128</a>
</div>

