<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/52739452" target="_blank" data-id="13314192" data-za-element-name="Title">
自学前端四个月怎么样才能找到一个实习？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/52739452/answer/135720155">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="49811170">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="135720155"> -->

